==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A very [[bad]] or [[scary]] [[dream]].
#:''I had a '''nightmare''' that I tried to run but not could not move or breathe.''
# {{figurative}} Any [[bad]], [[miserable]], [[difficult]] or [[terrify]]ing situation or experience that arouses severe [[anxiety]], [[terror]] or [[agony]].
#:''Cleaning up after identity theft can be a '''nightmare''' of phone calls and letters.''

